## Third-Party Components

### Z80 CPU Emulator
- **Source:** Marat Fayzullin (http://fms.komkon.org/EMUL8/)
- **License:** Freeware for non-commercial use
- **Files:** `components/z80_cpu/src/*`
- **Copyright:** Copyright (C) Marat Fayzullin 1994-2007

### ESP-IDF Framework
- **Source:** Espressif Systems (https://github.com/espressif/esp-idf)
- **License:** Apache License 2.0
- **Usage:** Build system and hardware abstraction

### Galagino Reference
- **Source:** Till Harbaum (https://github.com/harbaum/galagino)
- **License:** MIT License
- **Usage:** Reference implementation patterns

## ROM Files Disclaimer

**ROM files are NOT included** in this repository and must be obtained legally from the original Pac-Man arcade hardware or legitimate sources. This project does not distribute copyrighted ROM files.

Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with copyright laws when obtaining and using ROM files.

## Hardware Compatibility

This project is designed specifically for the Waveshare ESP32-C6-LCD-1.69 development board and may not work on other hardware configurations.